{"tid":1391545,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港中大隊員受壓需改名","createTime":"2019-07-31T13:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T13:06:54.000Z","uid":81228,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"37721b7a862db306b62aeac8ea56ee0d1c90334c","tid":1391545,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3091400/org/5b51ebe7002f3b74aa49e1d3bfd960d5.jpg/XI8L4c0XSWMRn9AILKKFVd-ku0qEVB9jPwQogBUEKIA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3091400%2Forg%2F5b51ebe7002f3b74aa49e1d3bfd960d5.jpg%2FXI8L4c0XSWMRn9AILKKFVd-ku0qEVB9jPwQogBUEKIA&h=d24c60e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3091410/org/cde7b4ccfc62fe1cff5c19c3f60d374b.jpg/twCYLFP-ATKp-9-FyvwTS7x9yIM5fpPgrrN6BISzegQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3091410%2Forg%2Fcde7b4ccfc62fe1cff5c19c3f60d374b.jpg%2FtwCYLFP-ATKp-9-FyvwTS7x9yIM5fpPgrrN6BISzegQ&h=6ca3f96f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3091411/org/ebf57490acb60018c4fe06dac0ba28b0.jpg/dtfpOl9gCZzd6J7FMZX5Zy2Q9Kgpo5VmTVq3rmdat64\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3091411%2Forg%2Febf57490acb60018c4fe06dac0ba28b0.jpg%2FdtfpOl9gCZzd6J7FMZX5Zy2Q9Kgpo5VmTVq3rmdat64&h=bbbfb6a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3091412/org/b6ceb4450ce79b616090433cc10be862.jpg/KU2ZN_1XrjT7jDp6M695ANGtkqWrkAJ-aYQrYUOEK2E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3091412%2Forg%2Fb6ceb4450ce79b616090433cc10be862.jpg%2FKU2ZN_1XrjT7jDp6M695ANGtkqWrkAJ-aYQrYUOEK2E&h=fa27fa49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3091401/org/334cf1aed8c48777f732b9bdeddfcaaf.jpg/HuGY9m5VHlzSFihzi1afIdGwHKj4HSGYILkMUQq5DFE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3091401%2Forg%2F334cf1aed8c48777f732b9bdeddfcaaf.jpg%2FHuGY9m5VHlzSFihzi1afIdGwHKj4HSGYILkMUQq5DFE&h=dbb79a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3091402/org/5f2af621b97754a04ea02ad4ee2c8f1a.jpg/XmLlQEkw39Su9t5_ajY77GNi1kmi_p-oj3lIbaV5SG0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3091402%2Forg%2F5f2af621b97754a04ea02ad4ee2c8f1a.jpg%2FXmLlQEkw39Su9t5_ajY77GNi1kmi_p-oj3lIbaV5SG0&h=ff4c1b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3091403/org/da2439de805db70ed3c92f4c8af3f6ab.jpg/9U6zop5zKcCRx_98GooSQZ9olkctERr0iHBOj6JwTo8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3091403%2Forg%2Fda2439de805db70ed3c92f4c8af3f6ab.jpg%2F9U6zop5zKcCRx_98GooSQZ9olkctERr0iHBOj6JwTo8&h=667c6b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019《英雄聯盟》全球高校冠軍盃今日（28日）於香港電競音樂節圓滿結束，上屆冠軍集美大學在決賽直落三局擊敗「黑馬」瑪麗維爾大學，成功衛冕高校盃。<br />\n<br />\n香港代表香港中文大學於八強出局，但今屆賽事早早在初賽階段便發生「改名事件」風波，令中大未能於整個賽事中聲援香港人，但隊中AD家希表示：「逼使大會要求我們改名，令『改名』一事有所迴響，已達到賽前目標。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然6名香港代表在最後一個比賽日毋需參賽，但亦有到場觀看決賽。家希認為冠軍集美大學擁有傳統中國電競隊的特質&mdash;&mdash;選擇前期強勢的英雄，於前期不斷開打，令對手難以發育，從而贏到最後，集美大學於決賽亦是靠同樣方法取勝。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>被大會警告　須刪去「政治敏感」數字 </strong><br />\n<br />\n「英雄聯盟校際盃」大專組在本月中上演時，參賽隊伍有人將遊戲名稱改成含有近月社運元素，例如理大代表的「香港黑警爆市民頭」，而中大代表於奪得冠軍後揚言「入世界賽會為香港人發聲」，要將遊戲名稱改成港人「五大訴求」。在世界賽高校盃初賽，他們在自己的遊戲名稱後加上「0609」、「0612」、「0616」、「0701」等數字，代表近期香港社會運動的日子。於首場比賽過後，他們收到大會警告，要求他們改成沒有數字的名稱。<br />\n<br />\n中大代表「馮迪生」黃萬修憶述當時情況，「首場初賽我們在遊戲名稱後加上數字。比賽完結後，我們被大會警告，因政治敏感為由要求我們改名，而且千萬不要在台上展示任何標語。雖然大會沒有提及後果，但我相信違抗他們的下場是DQ（取消資格）。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中大代表：逼使改名反獲迴響　做到賽前效果</strong><br />\n<br />\n另一名隊友家希起初亦有為「改名」一事反駁大會，「難道我喜歡這個日期也不能嗎？」然而，最後衡量到各方風險，還是選擇改名，「我們深知他們是比賽主辦商，事實上他們有權力要求我們改名（刪去數字）。然而，我認為大會這樣禁止我們改名（加上數字）反而是一件好事，因為證明此事已成功製造迴響，做到我們賽前的效果。」雖然未能以「完整名稱」完成賽事，但中大隊員都希望聲援港人。<br />\n<br />\nCGA行政總裁周啟康表明機構專注節目製作，對「改名」一事箇中細節並不清楚，至於主辦商Riot Games則拒絕受訪。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：徐焌然<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/357277/%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E9%AB%98%E6%A0%A1%E7%9B%83-%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%A1%9B%E5%86%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E9%9A%8A%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%97%E5%A3%93%E9%9C%80%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2F357277%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%259B%2584%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E7%259B%2583-%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%2586%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25A3%2593%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2590%258D&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFr7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=d7f8a2df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/357277/%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E9%AB%98%E6%A0%A1%E7%9B%83-%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%A1%9B%E5%86%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E9%9A%8A%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%97%E5%A3%93%E9%9C%80%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D</a>"},{"pid":"247ccb3e1d0bcc009241f85ab31a460c457acace","tid":1391545,"uid":135461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"Riot比騰訊買左 唔意外"},{"pid":"6f05786fe4de1ec5d61a8f17ceb192f1e6bd3309","tid":1391545,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"}]}